\caption{Top: Comparison of the Stokes V profiles obtained by selecting photospheric lines of low (red thin line) and high (green thin line) magnetic sensitivity for $\beta$ UMa. The thick red and green lines represent a moving average over three spectral bins of the thin lines. Center: same figure for $\theta$ Leo. Bottom: same for $\alpha^2$ CVn. All profiles are normalized to the continuum level.}
